<varlistentry id="options.TitleBevel">
	<term>TitleBevel</term>
	<listitem>
		<para>Determines the bevel to be drawn around the title bar. If you wish to have different
		bevels, depending on the window s state, use TitleFocusedBevel, TitleUnfocusedBevel or TitleStickyBevel.</para>
		<para>See Also: <ulink url="Bevel#synopsis">Bevel flags</ulink> for further details.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
